<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="425" type="etymology">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="425">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="425">Named in honor of Dr. Ralph W. Holzenthal, for a long and robust career in caddisfly taxonomy and systematics. Dr. Holzenthal has been a friend and colleague to each of the authors, and an invaluable mentor in particular to the first author.</paragraph>
